headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Robinhood Markets (HOOD) After A 200% One Year Surge?
summary: If you are wondering whether Robinhood Markets at around US$121.70 is priced for more growth or already reflects the story, you are not alone. The stock has a 5.4% return over the last week, a 7.8% decline over the last 30 days, and sits on a 5.6% year to date gain with a very large 1 year return of 200% and a multi year return of around 13x over 3 years.
